@startuml
title Commercial Catalog Context

rectangle "auth_service" as auth
rectangle "course_service" as course
rectangle "commercial_catalog_service" as catalog
rectangle "payments_service" as payments
rectangle "bonus_wallet_service" as bonus
rectangle "attribution-service" as attribution
rectangle "web_app / admin_app" as web

web --> catalog : public/admin API
payments --> catalog : internal offer lookup
catalog --> course : course snapshot lookup

payments --> bonus : bonus quote/commit
payments --> attribution : referral context

note right of catalog
Owns commercial offers,
bundle offers,
catalog price snapshot
and promo labels.
end note

@enduml
